OL,3,CPrince of Wales congratulates Aston
OL,4,CVilla after Europa League final victory
OL,6,FThe Prince of Wales has congratulated
OL,7,FAston Villa for their victory in the
OL,8,FEuropa League final in Istanbul,
OL,9,Fmarking their first European trophy in
OL,10,F44 years.
OL,12,FWilliam, patron of the Football
OL,13,FAssociation and a passionate Villa
OL,14,Fsupporter, erupted into cheers and
OL,15,Fcelebrated as the Birmingham-based
OL,16,Fside beat Freiburg 3-0 on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
