OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779393955
OL,3,CPrince of Wales congratulates Aston
OL,4,CVilla after Europa League final victory
OL,6,FIt was Villa's first major European
OL,7,Ffinal since the prince was born, their
OL,8,Ffirst silverware since the League Cup
OL,9,Fin 1996 and a first continental trophy
OL,10,Fsince the European Cup in 1982.
OL,12,FAfter the match, Kensington Palace
OL,13,Fpublished the Prince of Wales' message
OL,14,Fto the team: "Amazing night!!
OL,16,F"Huge congratulations to all the
OL,17,Fplayers, team, staff and everyone
OL,18,Fconnected to the club! 44 years since
OL,19,Fthe last taste of European silverware!"
OL,26,@vD@NOUxD@AOU{D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
