PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779393955
OL,3,CPrince of Wales congratulates Aston
OL,4,CVilla after Europa League final victory
OL,6,FThe prince added: "Special shout out
OL,7,Fto Boubacar Kamara who has been out
OL,8,Finjured but is such an integral part
OL,9,Fof our team and helped lay the
OL,10,Ffoundations of this success."
OL,12,FMidfielder Kamara has been absent
OL,13,Fsince suffering a knee injury earlier
OL,14,Fthis year.
OL,16,FAfter lifting the trophy, Villa
OL,17,Fcaptain John McGinn said that William,
OL,18,Fwho has followed the club since he was
OL,19,Fa schoolboy, met the players before
OL,20,Fkick-off.
OL,26,@nD@SOUrD@]O]
