OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779393955
OL,3,CPrince of Wales congratulates Aston
OL,4,CVilla after Europa League final victory
OL,6,F"He is a classy guy," McGinn told TNT.
OL,8,F"He was in the dressing room before
OL,9,Fthe game. He is a massive Villa fan so
OL,10,Fhe was never going to miss it.
OL,12,F"He is just a normal guy. It's great
OL,13,Fto have his support and hopefully it
OL,14,Fcontinues and tonight he can have a
OL,15,Fcouple of drinks with us and maybe get
OL,16,Fhis credit card out at the end of the
OL,17,Fnight."
OL,19,FDuring the final, Youri Tielemans and
OL,20,FEmiliano Buendia each scored a goal at
OL,21,Fthe end of the first half.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@UO]pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@GO]
